channel.title: Error fixing
channel.description:
if you get this error:
ERROR: client.java:29343: invalid methood declaration; return type required public int GetStanowner ;bim(int id) {
Remove the " ;bim".
and you get these errors: then get error: cannot find symbol. playerSE = GetStanowner ;bim(WearID); ^
cannot find symbol. playerSE = GetStanowner ;bim(WearID); ^
cannot find symbol. playerSE = GetStanowner ;bim(WearID); ^
cannot find symbol. playerSE = GetStanowner ;bim(WearID); ^
cannot find symbol. playerSE = GetStanowner ;bim(Playerequipment[playerwepon]); ^
OTHER SOLUTION:
then: Remove the " ;bim" for them all.
anyone get helped by this?
